data.enText: a feeling of friendship between people who do things together or share an interest

data.chText: （具有共同利益、目的或信仰的）团体，协会，联谊会
data.enText: an organized group of people who share an interest, aim or belief
the position of being a senior member of a college or university
an award of money to a graduate student to allow them to continue their studies or to do research

data.chText: （学术或专业团体的）会员资格
data.enText: the state of being a member of an academic or professional organization

data.chText: 当选为英国人文社会科学院的院士
data.enText: to be elected to fellowship of the British Academy

simple_means.memory_skill: fellow 伙伴 + ship 某种关系 → 交情

means: (具有共同利益、目的或信仰的)团体，协会，联谊会

ex.chText: 她所处的社交圈子很排外。
ex.enText: She was part of an exclusive social circle.
He is well-known in political circles.

synonyms.bx: 指由相互认识、定期会面的人组成的群体，也可指有着类似兴趣或工作的一群人。

ex.chText: 我们成立了一个帮助残障人士的协会。
ex.enText: We have formed an association to help the disabled.
He wanted to join the teachers' association.

synonyms.bx: 指有共同志向的人联合起来成立的正式组织。

ex.chText: 俱乐部投票同意接纳6名新成员。
ex.enText: The club has voted to admit 6 new members.

ex.chText: 球员们都穿着带有他们俱乐部标识的短上衣。
ex.enText: The players all have jackets with the club badge on them.

synonyms.bx: 指有着共同兴趣的人为了一起进行社交、娱乐、体育等活动而结成的组织。

ex.enText: She was finally granted a fellowship.

synonyms.bx: 指有共同利益、目的或信仰的人所组成的群体。

tr: an association of people who share common beliefs or activities
example: the message was addressed not just to employees but to every member of the company family
the church welcomed new members into its fellowship

tr: money granted (by a university or foundation or other agency) for advanced study or research
the state of being with someone
example: he enjoyed the society of his friends

value.def: A fellowship is a group of people that join together for a common purpose or interest.

example.tran: 国家精神分裂研究协会

example.ex: At Merlin's instigation, Arthur founds the Fellowship of the Round Table.
example.tran: 在梅林的建议下，亚瑟王创建了圆桌骑士团。

value.tran: (有共同目的或利益的)团体，协会，联谊会

value.def: A fellowship at a university is a post which involves research work.

example.ex: He was offered a research fellowship at Clare College.
example.tran: 他在克莱尔学院得到了一个研究员职位。

value.def: Fellowship is a feeling of friendship that people have when they are talking or doing something together and sharing their experiences.
